(Match 117)  12th February 1921  (British Championship)
SCOTLAND - WALES  2-1  (1-1)
Referee:   James Mason (England)
Crowd:     20.824, Pittodrie Park, Aberdeen
Goals:     1-0 Wilson (11), 1-1 Collier (30), 2-1 Wilson (46) 
SCOTLAND:
